It is caused by retention of oily secretion in the glands at the eyelid margin and subsequently induces a granulomatous reaction. Symptoms include a roundish painless lump over the eyelid in the form of a single or multiple nodule(s). If infected it may become red swollen and painful. 治療 C眼挑針早期細小時可用熱敷促進局部 血液流通兼用抗生素眼藥水/眼藥膏 有助消散炎症 如膿點未形成則可把發炎的眼睫毛拔 治療 如粒腫細小也許會隨分泌物自行流 出。如腺體受細菌感染粒腫便會紅腫 及有疼痛感。粒腫生長較大會有壓迫感 和影響美觀。醫生會採用局部麻醉在眼 驗內(結膜面施行一小切口把腫粒 內聚積物挖出。切口不需用縫線三數 天內會自行癒合 掉 Treatment Spontaneous recovery is possible for small nodules. If the nodule is large unsighty or infected surgical incision and curettage can be carried out under local or topical anesthesia as an out-patient procedure. It requires no suturing and the wound will heal within a few days 如膿腫不能消散切勿擠壓令膿腫擴 散。應待膿點受控制後才可切開排膿 (挑瘤)然後繼續用藥再加熱敷治療 老年人如於同一位置內多次復發醫生 會把挖出聚積組織送交病理檢查 If the nodule recurs at the same site in elderly patients excisional biopsy may be required to exclude malignancy C小兒一般需採用全身麻醉切除霉粒腫 如有其他疑問可於覆診時向醫 生查詢 C For the young infant/kids general anesthesia may be required
